description:
# Task: Remove Clerk from DashboardLayout.astro

## Parent Epic
legacy-897: EPIC: Complete ClerkJS Removal and Authentication Cleanup

## Objective
Remove all ClerkJS authentication code from the dashboard layout including SDK loading, inline auth scripts, and auth check logic.

## File Details
**Location**: `/home/paulo/sources/jng/legacy/src/layouts/DashboardLayout.astro`
**Lines**: 257 lines
**Purpose**: Layout for member/dashboard pages with authentication enforcement

## Sections to Remove

### 1. Environment Variable (Lines 50-51)
**Current Code**:
```typescript
const clerkPublishableKey =
  import.meta.env.PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY || 'pk_live_Y2xlcmsuam9ibmFncmluZ2EuY29tLmJyJA';
```
**Action**: Delete these lines

### 2. Props Interface Update (Lines 32-39)
**Current Props**:
```typescript
interface Props {
  title: string;
  description?: string;
  currentPage?: string;
  requiresAuth?: boolean;
  requiresPaidMembership?: boolean;
  noIndex?: boolean;
}
```
**Action**: Remove `requiresAuth` and `requiresPaidMembership` props

### 3. Props Destructuring Update (Lines 41-47)
**Current Code**:
```typescript
const {
  title,
  description = '',
  currentPage = 'dashboard',
  requiresAuth = true,
  requiresPaidMembership = false,
} = Astro.props;
```
**Action**: Remove `requiresAuth` and `requiresPaidMembership`

### 4. Clerk SDK Script (Lines 89-90)
**Current Code**:
```html
<!-- Clerk Authentication (async - critical for dashboard auth) -->
<script is:inline async crossorigin="anonymous" data-clerk-publishable-key={clerkPublishableKey} src="https://clerk.jobnagringa.com.br/npm/@clerk/clerk-js@5/dist/clerk.browser.js"></script>
```
**Action**: Delete entire script block

### 5. Inline Clerk Auth Script (Lines 91-103)
**Current Code**: Large minified inline script containing:
- COOKIE_NAME, LOCAL_KEY, COOKIE_TTL constants
- setCookie, persistUserData, getUserFromCookie, userShouldBeLoggedIn, userIsPaidCustomer, populateFirstNameFromUser, handleCommunityContent, runDomFuncs functions
- Clerk.load() initialization IIFE

**Action**: Delete entire `<script is:inline>` block (lines 91-103)

### 6. Auth Check Script (Lines 201-206)
**Current Code**:
```html
<!-- Auth check script -->
{requiresAuth && (
  <script is:inline>
    userShouldBeLoggedIn();
  </script>
)}
```
**Action**: Delete entire conditional block

### 7. Paid Membership Check Script (Lines 208-213)
**Current Code**:
```html
<!-- Paid membership check script -->
{requiresPaidMembership && (
  <script is:inline>
    !function(){function e(){...}function t(){...}if(!t()){window.location.href="/"}}();
  </script>
)}
```
**Action**: Delete entire conditional block

### 8. Logout Handler Script (Lines 227-252)
**Current Code**:
```html
<!-- Logout handler (inline - small and critical for UX) -->
<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const logoutBtn = document.getElementById('logout');
    if (logoutBtn) {
      logoutBtn.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        // Clear user cookie
        document.cookie = 'user=; path=/; max-age=0; domain=.jobnagringa.com.br';
        document.cookie = 'user=; path=/; max-age=0';
        // Clear localStorage
        try { localStorage.removeItem('user'); } catch(e) {}
        // Sign out from Clerk if available
        if (window.Clerk && Clerk.signOut) {
          Clerk.signOut().then(function() {
            window.location.href = '/';
          }).catch(function() {
            window.location.href = '/';
          });
        } else {
          window.location.href = '/';
        }
      });
    }
  });
</script>
```
**Action**: Delete entire script block

## Docstring Updates (Lines 1-22)
Remove references to:
- "Clerk authentication scripts" (line 14)
- "requiresAuth" prop documentation (line 20)
- "requiresPaidMembership" prop documentation (line 21)

## Comment Updates
Update the GTM comment block to remove Clerk reference:
**Before** (line 69-71): "Clerk Authentication (async - critical for dashboard auth)"
**After**: Remove this comment

## Pages Affected
These pages use DashboardLayout and pass auth props:
- `src/pages/jng/member-dashboard.astro`
- `src/pages/jng/jobs.astro`
- `src/pages/jng/community.astro`
- `src/pages/jng/course.astro`
- Other pages under `/jng/*`

These pages will need their props updated to remove requiresAuth/requiresPaidMembership.

## Verification
```bash
# Check no Clerk references remain
grep -n "clerk" src/layouts/DashboardLayout.astro
grep -n "Clerk" src/layouts/DashboardLayout.astro
grep -n "requiresAuth" src/layouts/DashboardLayout.astro

# Verify TypeScript
npm run check

# Test build
npm run build
```

## Estimated Lines Removed
~70 lines (from 257 to ~187 lines)
